    <item>
      <title>特朗普的“文化捍卫者”将重塑司法部民权部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/trump-s-culture-defender-set-to-remake-doj-civil-rights-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[司法部民权部门几十年来一直致力于保护种族、民族、宗教少数群体以及妇女的权利——这些群体是美国非法歧视的最常见受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/trump-s-culture-defender-set-to-remake-doj-civil-rights-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西客车与卡车相撞 致38人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/urgent-22-people-die-in-a-crash-between-a-passenger-bus-and-a-truck-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圣保罗（美联社）——官员称，周六凌晨，巴西东南部米纳斯吉拉斯州一条高速公路上一辆客车与一辆卡车相撞，造成 38 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/urgent-22-people-die-in-a-crash-between-a-passenger-bus-and-a-truck-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 13:55:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚圣诞节慈善活动发生踩踏事件 造成 13 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/urgent-10-people-including-children-die-in-stampede-in-nigeria-at-a-christmas-charity-event</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布贾，尼日利亚（美联社）——警方周六称，尼日利亚两起踩踏事件造成至少 13 人死亡，其中包括 4 名儿童，当时大批人群聚集在一起领取在一年一度的圣诞节活动中分发的食物和衣物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/urgent-10-people-including-children-die-in-stampede-in-nigeria-at-a-christmas-charity-event</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 13:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从也门发射的火箭弹击中特拉维夫地区；16 人受轻伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/rocket-fired-from-yemen-strikes-an-area-of-tel-aviv-overnight-16-people-lightly-injured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列特拉维夫（美联社）——以色列军方周六称，一枚从也门发射的火箭弹夜间击中特拉维夫地区，造成 16 人被碎玻璃伤。几天前，以色列空袭袭击了胡塞叛军，这些叛军一直在发射导弹声援加沙的巴勒斯坦人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/rocket-fired-from-yemen-strikes-an-area-of-tel-aviv-overnight-16-people-lightly-injured</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 07:39:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥学区首席执行官因市长与工会冲突被解雇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/chicago-education-board-fires-ceo-pedro-martinez-after-union-mayor-feud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥教育委员会周五采取了一项非同寻常的举措，解雇了该学区的首席执行官佩德罗·马丁内斯 (Pedro Martinez)，这是马丁内斯与市长之间长达数月的争执的一个戏剧性进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/chicago-education-board-fires-ceo-pedro-martinez-after-union-mayor-feud</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 03:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登签署美国支出协议以避免政府关门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-passes-plan-to-fund-government-as-shutdown-deadline-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登签署了拨款法案，以确保美国政府运转至 3 月中旬，避免年底关闭政府，并将未来的支出决定权交由唐纳德·特朗普担任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-passes-plan-to-fund-government-as-shutdown-deadline-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 23:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
